### Create Task

POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title":"Design Homepage",
  "description":"Create homepage wireframe",
  "project":"PROJECT_ID",
  "priority":"High",
  "status":"Todo",
  "labels":["design","ui"]
}

###

GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/project/PROJECT_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

PUT http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/TASK_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title":"Updated Task",
  "priority":"Medium"
}

###

PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/TASK_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status":"In Progress"
}

###

DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/TASK_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN